{"tid":2516860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟擬訂新法例　防止中資併購歐洲企業及參與投標","createTime":"2021-05-05T02:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T02:47:12.000Z","uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b927267460e7f6fe429846ada5d38a5fb1c1e396","tid":2516860,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:43:04.000Z","msg":"歐盟擬訂新法例　防止中資併購歐洲企業及參與投標<br />\n<br />\n歐盟據報將會實施新法例，防止中資併購歐洲企業及參與投標。德國《南德意志報》報道，歐盟執委會將於今日建議立法，阻止獲得政府補貼的外國企業併購歐盟企業、或參與歐盟的公開招標。報道表示，雖然條文未有指名是中國，只有在註腳和說明提到中國，但外界都認為，法例主要針對中資企業。報道表示，歐盟執委會認為，外國企業獲政府補貼併購歐盟企業，或破壞公平競爭的例子愈來愈多，有扭曲市場的風險。不過，按照歐盟的立法程序，執委會提出法案後，仍需經過歐洲議會和部長會議批准，數年後才會實施。<br />\n<br />\n2021-05-05 10:39:01<br />\n<br />\n[url]https://ne<del><a href=\"http://ws.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fws.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F158&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=2ccf73cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ws.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/158</a></del>9292-20210505.htm?spTabChangeable=0[/url]"},{"pid":"c7e7bf52cf938d3c99fd75d21ea22d820d5bcedc","tid":2516860,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:44:02.000Z","msg":"石頭、腳<br />\n玩火自焚<br />\n歷史倒車"},{"pid":"09aa4d492c797f74b83afb0bcd19338da92b7156","tid":2516860,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/09/maxresdefault-4-22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fmaxresdefault-4-22.jpg&h=36b71f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/08/600x400-GettyImages-866170226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F600x400-GettyImages-866170226.jpg&h=a7ff290b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}